\end_inset

 towards models that validate the principle of effective demand on the long-run which non-capacity creating expenditure leads the long run growth rate and capacity utilization converge to its normal level. In addition, the Kaleckian alternative that includes autonomous expenditures that do not create capacity initiated by 
